e ==\n'''\"Rabba Sacheya'''\" is synonymous with [[Faiz Ahmad Faiz]]'s poem. This song revolves around corruption in society and the struggle to keep a poor man alive. \"'''Meri Kahani'''\" song relates to lost memories, childhood and nostalgia. Piano is used in the song \"'''Mann Hota Hai'''\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531000533/http://www.gibsonguitar.in/News-Lifestyle/Features/hi-in/Atif-Aslams-Top-10-Non-Film-Songs.aspx|title=Atif Aslam\u2019s Top 10 Non-Film Songs|date=2012-05-31|website=web.archive.org|access-date=2020-04-15}}</ref>\n\n== Track Listing ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!No.\n!Song\n!Duration\n|-\n|01\n|Meri Kahani\n|03:39\n|-\n|02\n|Kinara\n|04:22\n|-\n|03\n|Rabba Sacheya\n|04:38\n|-\n|04\n|Mann Hota Hai\n|03:52\n|-\n|05\n|Joug\n|05:57\n|-\n|06\n|Chhod Gaye\n|03:31\n|-\n|07\n|Humrahi\n|05:31\n|-\n|08\n|Mae Ni\n|05:11\n|-\n|09\n|Kaun Tha: Kapkapi\n|03:34\n|-\n|10\n|Chhod Gaye (version 2)\n|03:51\n|-\n|11\n|Yaaro\n|03:36\n|-\n|12\n|Hungami Halaat [https://rateyourmusic.com/release/album/atif_aslam/meri_kahani/]\n|03:24\n|}\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n== External Links ==\n\n* Atif Aslam Official Website\n* Meri Kahani Album on YouTube\n", "name_user": "CAPTAIN RAJU", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up, addeduncategorisedtag", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meri_Kahani_(album)"}
{"title_page": "Play Hard", "text_new": "{{Infobox song\n| name       = Play Hard\n| cover      = Guetta - Play Hard single.jpg\n| alt        =\n| border     = yes\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[David Guetta]] featuring [[Ne-Yo]] and [[Akon]]\n| album      = [[Nothing but the Beat#2.0 Singles|Nothing but the Beat 2.0]]\n| released   = 22 September 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/Play-Hard-feat-Ne-Yo-Akon/dp/B00BV56NA4/ref=dm_att_trk7 |title=Play Hard (feat. Ne-Yo & Akon) [New Edit&#93;: David Guetta |publisher=Amazon.de |accessdate=2013-04-26}}</ref>\n| format     = {{hlist|[[CD single|CD]]|[[Music download|digital download]]}}\n| recorded   = 2012\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{hlist|[[Electro house]]|[[dance-pop]]}}\n| length     = {{ubl|3:21}} 3:28 {{small|(New Edit)}}\n| label      = [[Parlophone]]\n| writer     = {{hlist|[[Ne-Yo|Shaffer Smith]]|[[Akon|Aliaune Thiam]]|[[David Guetta]]|Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Riesterer|Giorgio Tuinfort|[[Alice DeeJay|Sebastiaan Molijn]]|[[Alice DeeJay|Eelke Kalberg]]}}\n| producer   = {{hlist|David Guetta|Giorgio Tuinfort|Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Riesterer}}\n| chronology = [[David Guetta]]\n| prev_title = [[Just One Last Time]]\n| prev_year  = 2012\n| next_title = [[Right Now (Rihanna song)|Right Now]]\n| next_year  = 2013\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[Ne-Yo]]\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = [[Forever Now (Ne-Yo song)|Forever Now]]\n | prev_year  = 2012\n | title      = Play Hard\n | year       = 2012\n | next_title = [[Tonight (Jessica Sanchez song)|Tonight]]\n | next_year  = 2013\n}}\n{{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[Akon]]\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = [[Like Money (song)|Like Money]]\n | prev_year  = 2012\n | title      = Play Hard\n | year       = 2012\n | next_title = Interstellar\n | next_year  = 2015\n}}\n{{External music video|{{YouTube|5dbEhBKGOtY|\"Play Hard\"}}}}\n{{Audio sample\n | type        = single\n | file        = David Guetta - Play Hard.ogg\n | description = 13 second sample from David Guetta's \"Play Hard\"\n}}\n}}\n\n\"'''Play Hard'''\" is a song by jew [[disc jockey|DJ]] and record producer [[David Guetta]] featuring vocals from American singers [[Ne-Yo]] and [[Akon]]. It was released on 15 March 2013 as a single from the re-release of Guetta's fifth studio album, ''[[Nothing but the Beat]]'' (2011). This is the second collaboration between Guetta and Akon since \"[[Sexy Bitch]]\" in 2009. All three artists co-wrote the song along with Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Riesterer and Giorgio Tuinfort, both of whom produced the song with Guetta. Akon's vocals were written and recorded at [[Sonic Vista Studios]] in [[Ibiza]] in July 2012.{{Citation needed|date=March 2014}} The song samples the 1998 Eurodance song \"[[Better Off Alone (Alice Deejay song)|Better Off Alone]]\" by [[Alice Deejay]] and \"In My Dreams (XXL Remix)\" by [[Noemi (singer)|Noemi]]. \"Play Hard\" peaked at number six on the [[UK Singles Chart]], thus becoming his fourteenth top 10 hit in the UK as a lead artist. It also charted within the top 10 of the charts in several other countries including Austria, Belgium, Czech Republic, France, Germany, Ireland, Israel, Italy, Luxembourg, Poland, Scotland, Slovakia, South Korea, Spain and Switzerland; as well as the top 20 in Australia, Denmark, Finland, Iceland and New Zealand.\n\nGuetta reported on [[Twitter]] shortly before the release that he planned to release an edited version of \"Play Hard\" as the next single from ''Nothing but the Beat 2.0'' for a long while, which would make it the tenth single from ''Nothing but the Beat''.<ref>{{cite web|title=Back to the studio on Monday to finish the new version of play hard , my next single. It's sooooo big!|url=https://twitter.com/davidguetta/status/307880621370376193|work=Twitter|publisher=davidguetta|accessdate=8 March 2013}}</ref> This version never came to fruition, however.\n\n==Music video==\nAn official [[music video]] was uploaded to Guetta's official [[Vevo]] channel on April 22, 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5dbEhBKGOtY|title=David Guetta - Play Hard ft. Akon & Ne-Yo|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2013-04-22}}</ref> The video uses the New Edit version of the song. Directed by Swede [[Andreas Nilsson (film director)|Andreas Nilsson]],<ref>{{cite web |last=Taylor |first=Ken |url=http://news.beatport.com/blog/2013/04/24/david-guettas-play-hard-video-is-a-treasure-trove-of-high-art-influence/ |title=David Guetta's \"Play Hard\" video is a treasure trove of high-art influence \u2013 Beatport News |publisher=News.beatport.com |date=2013-04-24 |accessdate=2013-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130429201043/http://news.beatport.com/blog/2013/04/24/david-guettas-play-hard-video-is-a-treasure-trove-of-high-art-influence/ |archive-date=2013-04-29 |url-status=dead }}</ref> it generated controversy for its stereotypical portrayal of [[Mexico]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theclinic.cl/2013/04/26/el-ultimo-video-de-david-guetta-que-se-burla-de-los-estereotipos-mexicanos-ha-causado-polemica/|title=El \u00faltimo video de David Guetta que se burla de los estereotipos mexicanos ha causado pol\u00e9mica|publisher=The Clinic Online|accessdate=2013-04-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://informe21.com/arte-y-espectaculos/causa-polemica-el-nuevo-video-del-dj-david-guetta-%E2%80%9Cplay-hard%E2%80%9D|title=Causa pol\u00e9mica el nuevo video del Dj David Guetta \"Play hard\"|publisher=Informe21.com|accessdate=2013-04-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://entretenimiento.terra.com.pe/musica/david-guetta-crea-polemica-con-el-video-de-play-hard,2698df580215e310VgnCLD20000099cceb0aRCRD.html|title=David Guetta crea pol\u00e9mica con el video de 'Play Hard'|publisher=[[Terra Networks|Terra Pe\u00fa]]|accessdate=2013-04-28}}</ref> The video and an advertisement from Neon Mixr feature the popular dancers, [[Les Twins]]. The video has over 970 million views as of {{currentmonth}} {{currentyear}}.\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/Play-Hard-feat-Ne-Yo-Akon/dp/B00ADBTQN8/ref=sr_1_cc_2?s=aps&ie=UTF8&qid=1365581559&sr=1-2-catcorr&keywords=david+guetta+play+hard |title=Play Hard (feat. Ne-Yo & Akon): David Guetta |publisher=Amazon.de |accessdate=2013-04-26}}</ref>\n| title1 = Play Hard\n| length1 = 3:21\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/Play-Hard-feat-Ne-Yo-Akon/dp/B00BV56NA4/ref=sr_1_cc_1?s=aps&ie=UTF8&qid=1365581559&sr=1-1-catcorr&keywords=david+guetta+play+hard |title=Play Hard (feat. Ne-Yo & Akon) [New Edit&#93;: David Guetta |publisher=Amazon.de |accessdate=2013-04-26}}</ref>\n| title1 = Play Hard\n| note1 = New Edit\n| length1 = 3:28\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Digital download \u2013 EP<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B00BV56NVS/ref=dm_sp_alb?ie=UTF8&qid=1365581559&sr=1-3-catcorr |title=Play Hard (feat. Ne-Yo & Akon) [Remixes&#93;: David Guetta |publisher=Amazon.de |accessdate=2013-04-26}}</ref>\n| title1 = Play Hard\n| note1 = Albert Neve Remix\n| length1 = 6:52\n| title2 = Play Hard\n| note2 = R3hab Remix\n| length2 = 4:06\n| title3 = Play Hard\n| note3 = Maurizio Gubellini & Delayers In Da House Remix\n| length3 = 5:00\n| title4 = Play Hard\n| note4 = Maurizio Gubellini Remix\n| length4 = 5:11\n| title5 = Play Hard\n| note5 = Spencer & Hill Remix\n| length5 = 6:19\n| title6 = Play Hard\n| note6 = Extended\n| length6 = 5:12\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = German CD single<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/Play-Hard-Remixes-Guetta-David/dp/B00C7FWC2U/ref=sr_1_1?s=music&ie=UTF8&qid=1365581559&sr=1-1&keywords=david+guetta+play+hard |title=Play Hard (Remixes) |publisher=Amazon.de |accessdate=2013-04-26}}</ref>\n| title1 = Play Hard\n| note1 = Albert Neve Remix\n| length1 = 6:52\n| title2 = Play Hard\n| note2 = R